snippet.title: Canadian Prepper
snippet.description:
The purpose of this channel is to help more people get prepared for emergency situations. 

Innovative Gear reviews, discussions about the collapse of civilization as we know it, self-defense and all things preparedness from a Canadian perspective. SUBSCRIBE! 

Get the HIGHEST QUALITY Survival and Prepping Gear here (use discount code SURVIVALPREPPER for 10% off)
http://www.canadianpreparedness.com/
